==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Compunctious
<hw>Com*punc"tious</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of the nature
of compunction; caused by conscience; attended with, or causing,
compunction.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>That no <qex>compunctious</qex> visitings of nature⟦br⟧
Shake my fell purpose.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Compunctiously</ent>⟦br⟧
